Although the location is a little hard to find, the food, atmosphere, and staff were really great. My boyfriend and I ordered the bulgogi banh mi, the crackle pork belly bao, and the kimchi fries. Everything was incredible, although the fries were a definite standout. I would also recommend getting the Thai tea as well!
